Text: Thank you!  So glad to finally find this album!  Does anyone have his "Romeo and Juliet E.P." ?

Hey look! It's me!  I figured this would eventually end up on here.  Please do me a favor, if you're going to torrent my album, please go to iTunes or cdbaby and give me a nice rating and/or review.  And eventually if you someday have the means, buying the album would be groovy too.
